div.div: Lee Giho is trying to earn his tuition through the popular VR game Circuit, but things just aren't going his way. However, right when he decides to throw in the towel, he gets a lucky break that changes everything. Fortune leads him ever deeper into the games lore, and before he knows it, Giho finds himself stocked up with powerful items chasing an elusive group of mysterious warriors. But to unlock his true powers, Giho must learn the secrets of this group before his luck runs out for good. (Source: Tapas)

"If you wish to return, then you must find all the stones of the Dragon's Heart!" And so, Lee started his adventure to become an unparalleled mage. Which bonds will he find? That's all up to him, to discover...
